results.name: Smallest prime factor of n-th term in Look and Say sequence A005150, with a(1)=1.
comment: The terms in A005150 that are known to be primes are a(2) = 11, a(6) = 312211 and a(7) = 13112221 (A100108).
a(n) = 3 iff A004977(n) is positive and divisible by 3.
xref: Cf. A004977 (sum of digital digits of terms of A005150), A005150 (Look and Say sequence), A020639, A100108 (primes in Look and Say sequence).
results.author: _Bernard Schott_, Apr 15 2020
